'''Balmorra Flu''' was a mildly contagious form of the [[Flu/Legends|flu]] causing intense [[Sinuses|sinus]] pain and swelling, accompanied by the excessive production of mucus. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] once caught Balmorra Flu while on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Dantooine/Legends|Dantooine]].

